                </h1>
                <p class="text-base text-stone-500 pt-4 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg xl:text-xl">With this oracle, you can indisputably prove presence at a location, recorded permanently on-chain. Connect your Hashpack wallet to get started. 
                </p>
                <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-12">
                  <div class="sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-xl lg:mx-0">
                    <div class="sm:flex">
                      <div class="mt-3 sm:ml-3 sm:mt-0">
