                </svg>
                How it's indisputable.
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">Your device location data is stored on-chain using anonymous identifiers in smart contracts.</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-stone-400">
                <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-amber-700" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 1a4.5 4.5 0 00-4.5 4.5V9H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.5V5.5A4.5 4.5 0 0010 1zm3 8V5.5a3 3 0 10-6 0V9h6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
