            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-stone-400">
                <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-amber-700" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 2a5 5 0 00-5 5c0 3.25 5 10 5 10s5-6.75 5-10a5 5 0 00-5-5zm0 6.5a1.5 1.5 0 110-3 1.5 1.5 0 010 3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Location recording.
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">With each device beacon, a location is recorded on the ledger, updating the location state in the smart contract.</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-stone-400">
