                Advanced tracking. 
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">The ledger provides full auditability and physical traceability for historical analysis from the <a href="https://hashscan.io/testnet/contract/0.0.3643101" class="text-base text-stone-500 hover:text-stone-900 underline" target="_blank">Smart Contract on HashScan.</a></dd>
