                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/shelby-seeholzer-840101191/" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-400" target="_blank">
                      <span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span>
                      <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
